-Removal of JBoots dropping from Drezelna in Najena, instead making them only obtainable as a quest item.<br>
-Addition of a (working) alchemy skill, making sow speed available to everyone with plat, given enough time.<br>
-Items like manastones available as semi-easily campable, droppable items.<br>
<br>
